import React from 'react'
import About from './About'
import { Navbar, Nav } from 'react-bootstrap'
import { useState } from 'react'



function Main() {

  const [currentPage, setCurrentPage] = useState(1) //Variavel para re mudar as paginas

  return (
    <>
        <Navbar bg="dark" variant='dark'>
          <Navbar.Brand>Web Lucas</Navbar.Brand>
          <Nav>
            <Nav.Link onClick={() => {setCurrentPage(1);}}>Sobre</Nav.Link>
            <Nav.Link onClick={() => {setCurrentPage(2);}}>Anotações</Nav.Link>
            <Nav.Link onClick={() => {setCurrentPage(3);}}>Blog</Nav.Link>
            <Nav.Link onClick={() => {setCurrentPage(4);}}>Noticias</Nav.Link>
          </Nav>
        </Navbar>
        <About/>
    </>
  )
}

export default Main
